  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>51680</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_004_130_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Mel&gt;&lt;Mel&gt;～∀　さっきの、すんばらしいコンボだど～。
びぃしぃっと決まって、ナイスファイトだ～よ～</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Mel&gt;~ My goodness, what a superb combo!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>51784</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_004_130_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ひとりで沢山の魔物と戦える余裕が出てきたみたいです</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Looks like I can handle a lot more monsters on
my own, now.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>51900</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_004_130_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>どっかで、ボサーッと、遊んどる、
誰かさんとはえれー違いだ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Quite different from a certain someone else who
only seems to putz around like a careless child!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>52036</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_004_130_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……オ、オレはみんなの荷物持ってんだよ……
これをおまえサボってるってのか……！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...I...am CARRYING EVERYONE'S STUFF!
Are you slacking off on us now!?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>52156</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_004_130_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>荷物持ちじゃんけん勝負しようって
言いだしたの&lt;Dio&gt;だったよね……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You were the one who suggested Rock, Paper,
Scissors to see who was on luggage duty.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>52288</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_004_130_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>タンス野郎まで混ざるなんて聞いてねー！
こんないっぱいの服、押しつけやがって……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I didn't think the WARDROBE would be in on it!
He just forced this pile of laundry onto me...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>52416</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_004_130_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ん？　んだんだんだ？　ん？
っだら、もう一回勝負するだか？　ええだーよ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hmm? What's that you say? You wanna shoot
another round with ol' chiffy boy?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>52484</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_004_130_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>今度は負けねー！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh, I ain't losing THIS round--!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>52564</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_004_130_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>え？　わ、わたしもやるの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Huh? Wait, a-am I joining in, too?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>52664</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_004_130_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ったりめーだろ！　……行くぞ！
じゃん、けん……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's just how it goes! NOW!
Rock...Papper...SCISSORS...!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>52724</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_004_130_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>グー！！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Shoot!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>52832</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_004_130_012&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ぐぉっ！　ぐわっ！　いてっ！　あ、おい！
やめろっ……！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ga-- GUHWOH--! Ouch! S-stop!
Stop iiiit!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>52968</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_004_130_013&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ふぉぉぉっ……す、すげーだ……。
こ、ここに、コンボの鬼……鬼神がいるだーよ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Wooooooah... Sh-she's, a combo monster. Nay...
A combo GODDESS.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
</SceneText>
